---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="For Investors, Creators & Media">
    <main>
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>For Investors, Creators & Media: Explore the Future of Entertainment Technology</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Discover how "Living with the Ghost of Sam" creates unprecedented opportunities across the creative industry spectrum</p>
        </div>

        <section class="content">
            <div class="info-card vision">
                <h2>The Innovation Landscape</h2>
                <p>"Living with the Ghost of Sam" represents more than just a television seriesâ€”it's a pioneering framework for the ethical and creative application of AI technology in entertainment. Whether you're an investor seeking emerging markets, a creator developing similar concepts, or a journalist covering the entertainment technology revolution, this project offers invaluable insights into one of the industry's most transformative developments.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card audience-segments">
                <h2>Tailored Information For Your Interests</h2>
                <p>Select the category that best describes your focus to explore relevant opportunities:</p>
                
                <div class="segment-grid">
                    <div class="segment-card">
                        <h3>For Investors</h3>
                        <p>Explore the business model, market analysis, and revenue projections for technology that respectfully preserves and extends entertainment legacies.</p>
                        <a href="#investor-section" class="segment-link">Investor Information</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="segment-card">
                        <h3>For Creative Developers</h3>
                        <p>Discover our technological framework and how it might be applied to your own creative concepts involving legacy talent and AI integration.</p>
                        <a href="#creator-section" class="segment-link">Creator Information</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="segment-card">
                        <h3>For Media & Journalists</h3>
                        <p>Access background information, ethical considerations, and interview opportunities regarding this groundbreaking approach to entertainment technology.</p>
                        <a href="#media-section" class="segment-link">Media Resources</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="investor-section" class="info-card investor">
                <h2>For Investors: The Next Entertainment Frontier</h2>
                <div class="two-column">
                    <div>
                        <h3>Market Opportunity:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>$8.3B projected market for legacy content enhancement by 2027</li>
                            <li>Untapped potential in posthumous entertainment IP utilization</li>
                            <li>Technology with applications across film, television, gaming, and live events</li>
                            <li>First-mover advantage in an emerging content category</li>
                            <li>Multiple revenue streams from technology licensing and content creation</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Investment Advantages:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Scalable technology with diverse application potential</li>
                            <li>IP-driven business model with recurring revenue opportunities</li>
                            <li>Positive reception from entertainment industry stakeholders</li>
                            <li>Clear path to market with established production partners</li>
                            <li>Long-term value creation through expanding library of digital assets</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">83%</div>
                        <p>Of consumers express interest in new content featuring beloved deceased performers</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">5.2x</div>
                        <p>Projected ROI for initial technology development investment</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">$175M</div>
                        <p>Estimated value of series and associated technology IP by year three</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">12+</div>
                        <p>Distinct revenue streams from technology and content applications</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="creator-section" class="info-card creator">
                <h2>For Creative Developers: Build Upon Our Framework</h2>
                <p>Our technological and ethical frameworks offer valuable insights for creators developing similar concepts:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Structured approach to estate relationships and IP development</li>
                    <li>Technical solutions for integrating digital recreations with live performances</li>
                    <li>Narrative strategies for meaningful legacy integration</li>
                    <li>Ethical boundaries that respect the integrity of recreated performers</li>
                    <li>Production methodologies for cost-effective implementation</li>
                    <li>Audience engagement insights from extensive market research</li>
                </ul>
                
                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <h3>Licensing & Partnership Opportunities</h3>
                    <p>For creators with complementary concepts, we offer:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Technology licensing for projects outside our initial focus areas</li>
                        <li>Co-development partnerships for complementary properties</li>
                        <li>Consulting services for productions utilizing similar technologies</li>
                        <li>White-label implementation of our digital recreation platform</li>
                        <li>Access to our established relationships with estates and rights holders</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="media-section" class="info-card media">
                <h2>For Media & Journalists: The Complete Story</h2>
                <p>"Living with the Ghost of Sam" addresses fascinating questions at the intersection of technology, entertainment, and ethics:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>How can AI honor rather than exploit the legacies of beloved performers?</li>
                    <li>What safeguards ensure respectful digital recreation of deceased artists?</li>
                    <li>How is the entertainment industry adapting to these technological possibilities?</li>
                    <li>What does this technology mean for the future of performance and creativity?</li>
                    <li>How are audience reactions shaping this emerging entertainment category?</li>
                    <li>What precedents does this establish for digital rights after death?</li>
                </ul>
                
                <div class="resources-grid">
                    <div class="resource-card">
                        <h3>Available Resources</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Press kit with background information and visuals</li>
                            <li>Access to technology demonstrations and behind-the-scenes footage</li>
                            <li>Executive interviews with key production and technical leads</li>
                            <li>Estate representative perspectives on digital legacy management</li>
                            <li>Audience research data and market analysis</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="resource-card">
                        <h3>Story Angles</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>The technology behind bringing comedy legends back to life</li>
                            <li>Ethical frameworks for posthumous representation</li>
                            <li>The business of legacy management in the digital age</li>
                            <li>How AI is transforming entertainment production</li>
                            <li>Audience nostalgia as a driver for technological innovation</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card case-studies">
                <h2>Real-World Applications & Results</h2>
                <div class="case-grid">
                    <div class="case-card">
                        <h3>Technology Proof of Concept</h3>
                        <p>Our initial recreation of Sam Kinison's performance style demonstrated 94% audience recognition accuracy while maintaining full estate approval and satisfaction.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="case-card">
                        <h3>Estate Relationship Model</h3>
                        <p>We've developed a transparent compensation and approval framework that has been endorsed by representatives from seven major comedy estates.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="case-card">
                        <h3>Production Integration</h3>
                        <p>Test footage showing interaction between current actors and digital recreations has been rated "extremely convincing" by 87% of test audiences.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="case-card">
                        <h3>Market Validation</h3>
                        <p>Concept presentations to three major streaming platforms resulted in competitive interest and development commitments, confirming market demand.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card materials">
                <h2>Available Materials</h2>
                <div class="materials-grid">
                    <a href={`${base}investor-deck`} class="material-link">
                        <div class="material-card">
                            <h3>Investor Deck</h3>
                            <p>Comprehensive business model and projections</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href={`${base}tech-white-paper`} class="material-link">
                        <div class="material-card">
                            <h3>Technology White Paper</h3>
                            <p>Technical overview of our digital recreation platform</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href={`${base}press-kit`} class="material-link">
                        <div class="material-card">
                            <h3>Media Kit</h3>
                            <p>Press materials, images, and background information</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href={`${base}partnership-guide`} class="material-link">
                        <div class="material-card">
                            <h3>Partnership Guide</h3>
                            <p>Framework for creative and technology collaborations</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card contact">
                <h2>Connect With Our Team</h2>
                <p>Interested in exploring opportunities related to "Living with the Ghost of Sam"?</p>
                <div class="contact-grid">
                    <a href="mailto:investors@example.com" class="contact-btn">Investor Relations</a>
                    <a href="mailto:creators@example.com" class="contact-btn">Creative Partnerships</a>
                    <a href="mailto:press@example.com" class="contact-btn">Media Inquiries</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    main {
        color: white;
    }

    .hero {
        background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), url('/living-with-the-ghost-of-sam/images/SamImage.jpg') no-repeat center center;
        background-size: cover;
        padding: 4rem 2rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .hero h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin: 0;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .subtitle {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        opacity: 0.9;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .content {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
    }

    .info-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .info-card h2 {
        color: #FFD700;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .info-card h3 {
        color: #FFD700;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .info-card ul {
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .info-card li {
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .segment-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .segment-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        height: 100%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .segment-card h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
    }

    .segment-link {
        display: inline-block;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        color: white;
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 4px;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin-top: auto;
        transition: background-color 0.2s;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .segment-link:hover {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    }

    .highlight-box {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .highlight-box h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
    }

    .two-column {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .stats-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .stat-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        text-align: center;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .stat-number {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #FFD700;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .resources-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .resource-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .resource-card h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
    }

    .case-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .case-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .case-card h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
    }

    .materials-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .material-link {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
    }

    .material-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        transition: transform 0.2s, background-color 0.2s;
    }

    .material-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    .contact {
        text-align: center;
    }

    .contact-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 1.5rem auto 0;
    }

    .contact-btn {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #2196F3;
        color: white;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 4px;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: background-color 0.2s;
    }

    .contact-btn:hover {
        background: #1976D2;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .two-column, .segment-grid, .stats-grid, .resources-grid, .case-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .materials-grid, .contact-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>
